✨ Today we honor #Juneteenth — a historic day marking the end of slavery in the U.S. and a powerful reminder of the ongoing fight for freedom, justice, and equality.

🌍 While Juneteenth is rooted in U.S. history, its message reaches far beyond. It reminds us that the pursuit of dignity and equity is a global journey — one that aligns with our values at Algolia: trust, care, candor, humility, and grit.

🖤 Honoring Juneteenth means acknowledging the past, listening to lived experiences, and taking action toward a more inclusive future — in our communities, our workplaces, and around the world.

Tap the link in bio and join us in learning, reflecting, and showing up for equity and inclusion. #Juneteenth2025 #CelebrateFreedom #RacialEquity #JusticeForAll #EqualityForAll #FreedomDay #SocialImpact #Inclusion #AlgoliaValues
